I present you, an Actor that fails half the time. I call it, The Imperfect Actor.

Chapther I
The Imperfect Actor

The Imperfect Actor has the problem that it only responds half the time. How are we going to create a reliable way of communication, is the problem to fix.

### Reliable Communication
For this we are going to use the most updated pattern as of today, september of 2019. It is called Alpakka Transactions and it is the replacement for the 2018 way of doing things, the Journal Puller pattern.
. 2018 Journal Poller pattern
. 2019 Alpakka Transaction pattern

